15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 461 of Title 10, unless there is
18 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. There is hereby created until November 1, 2028, in
20 accordance with the Oklahoma Sunset Law, the Teacher Recruitment and
21 Retention Program to be administered by Oklahoma Partnership for
22 School Readiness.
23 B. The Program, through Oklahoma Partnership for School
24 Readiness, shall ensure that:
